{"tid":2157890,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯被西班牙媒體《阿斯報》打了零分","createTime":"2020-08-15T10:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T03:04:30.000Z","uid":173952,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"29c47a69bb599b7412dee0c911f249dbc33ba504","tid":2157890,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"在巴塞2比8慘遭拜仁橫掃後，西班牙媒體對巴塞球員的表現打出了多個零分。<br />\n<br />\n  《阿斯報》給出場的九名巴塞球員打了零分，其中就包括美斯，只有蘇亞雷斯和艾巴得到了分數，該報的大標題是：「歷史性的羞辱」。<br />\n<br />\n  《每日體育報》稱，這是一個「噩夢般的夜晚」，對巴塞教練施迪安，該報直接打出了一個詞：「解僱」。<br />\n<br />\n  《馬卡報》的大標題則是「可恥」，報導稱，這個賽季巴塞顆粒無收，這是繼2008年以來的第一次，是巴塞「一個輝煌時代的結束」。<br />\n<br />\n  《世界體育報》則稱，巴塞的這場2比8，是「慘敗中的慘敗」。"},{"pid":"a2ec5862554c0ba0988f6a529a1126c541b7c2fc","tid":2157890,"uid":219128,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dohMo3S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdohMo3S.png&h=4baaaa4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60d5ebbb5d5d38ec0b5d2dd2089eea4c4563f333","tid":2157890,"uid":1147,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"whoscored 係咪繼續俾滿分？"},{"pid":"382794d6f7db9e405c1a4ad14be4e4d5616eedf2","tid":2157890,"uid":199081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得迪莊都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b1db4593337043e93fcb653e071743c7efa7f1","tid":2157890,"uid":209773,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"瘋狂炒教練同啲非洲國家係咁換總統有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b08653a009c88d94c332c12ad93ea37cf7aad6","tid":2157890,"uid":313162,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48b1db4593337043e93fcb653e071743c7efa7f1","tid":2157890,"uid":209773,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"瘋狂炒教練同啲非洲國家係咁換總統有咩分別<img src=\"/a